{"tid":2122680,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"公司註冊處處長鍾麗玲接任私隱專員 曾被質疑政治審查黃店","createTime":"2020-07-24T06:38:28.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-24T09:52:41.000Z","uid":240362,"like":13,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3b55eb293fbece2328c277a19b4e65f709d02a56","tid":2122680,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T06:38:28.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200724/E72YPZ4GLDKBUM2XR7YR4YHYSU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200724%2FE72YPZ4GLDKBUM2XR7YR4YHYSU%2F&d=7JJHJI7m8dwGfBTVwC1i6Ay7VxIBYRqzliHj24KwcnI%3D&h=e67b0ff3\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200724%2FE72YPZ4GLDKBUM2XR7YR4YHYSU%2F&h=f0a380a3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200724/E72YPZ4GLDKBUM2XR7YR4YHYSU/</a><br />\n<br />\n目前鍾麗玲仍是公司註冊處處長，曾被質疑向黃店作政治審查。專門為抗爭者及良心僱主提供工作配對服務的晨光萬事屋，今年3月底向公司註冊處申請開設公司，其後收到公司註冊處信件，要求晨光14日內回覆解釋過往受訪的語錄，包括「手足」、「獨派」、「黃色經濟圈」及「抗戰」等字眼，被質疑是政治審查及打壓。"},{"pid":"9874ba8c0c2b791d56d0d79c9359d9084ceb92b7","tid":2122680,"uid":107577,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T06:39:17.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n隨時推上國際<br />\n香港唔洗再撈"},{"pid":"13e7d8ad73288f54f6eab68ac8cdb4b0a3aec5a3","tid":2122680,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9874ba8c0c2b791d56d0d79c9359d9084ceb92b7","tid":2122680,"uid":107577,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T06:39:17.000Z","msg":"推<br />\n隨時推上國際<br />\n香港唔洗再撈"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-24T06:41:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji